Text: ReRequest for telephone numberSera Thank you for your message My direct is and if I am not there my assistant Holly usually knows my schedule and how to track me down Also please know that although I grew up in Maine I consider Texas my home away from home Feel free to call anytime and please let Jeff know I look forward to meeting him via the telephone Sincerely Jane Jane Robinson Associate Director of Admissions Bay State Road Boston MA Reply Separator Subject Request for telephone number Author Date PM Ms Robinson Im writing on behalf of Jeff Skilling to whom Kay Cole introduced to you via email He would like to speak to you by phone regarding his daughter Kristins potential interest in attending Boston University Would you be willing to provide us with your phone number Please let us know if there is anything we can do to assist you with your future visits to Houston I looking forward to hearing from you soon Regards Sherri Sera Assistant to the President CEO fax
